ominant component. Moreover the relaxation of the vestige dynamo\nmagnetic field within the radiative core is found to satisfy MHD stability\ncriteria. Hence it does not experience a global reconfiguration but slowly\nrelaxes by retaining its mixed stable poloidal-toroidal topology.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Sep 2017 08:46:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-15"}
