anetary origin. Follow-up observations will be required to\nassess the possibility that the redshifted Ly{\\alpha} and Si iii absorption\nsignatures arise from interactions between the exospheric flow and the magnetic\nfield of the star.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Sep 2017 09:49:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-15"}
