arrival time can be determined in a redundant way. In this contribution, the\nmain features and the technical performance of the TIB are presented.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Sep 2017 10:12:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 17 Oct 2017 09:01:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-22"}
