t ~65Myr.\nUsing tau as a criterion, the current state-of-the-art solutions all differ\nfrom previously published results beyond ~50Myr. I also conducted an eigenmode\nanalysis, which provides some insight into the chaotic nature of the inner\nSolar System. The current study provides new orbital solutions for applications\nin geological studies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Sep 2017 15:44:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 29 Oct 2017 21:17:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-31"}
